coredns-filter
=============

CoreDNS[1] fork with a blocklist plugin added.

Domains blacklist is implemented via gravity.db[2] from the Pihole project.

Additionally, /etc/hosts-like file can be used as a DNS records source, 
which is useful for simple SOHO networks.


----
[1] https://github.com/coredns/coredns
[2] https://docs.pi-hole.net/database/gravity/
